{"tid":296684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜如風 黃翠如 邊個旅遊主持最正常？","createTime":"2017-06-24T18:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T01:39:38.000Z","uid":14730,"like":21,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1aae60ca602f405365abbebcc95f3b5f5146fd12","tid":296684,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:46:09.000Z","msg":"杜如風<br />\n不得不提她成名之作《流行東京》，以獨特風格而吸引人注意。由於她喜愛購物，加上豪邁爽朗的真性情性格，比起大台一向作狀及虛偽的旅遊節目，她所主持的旅遊節目更有新鮮感，更有看點！不過由於的言行比較過火，也引來不少人對她反感，指她一直曬命，指她是一名港女。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃翠如　<br />\n很多女主持未必像黃翠如一樣玩得起，她由有線到Now及直至今天的無綫，她每次主持的旅行節目投入度最強，在有線的《地平線上這個世界那些人》節目中，在土耳其泥漿浴上穿三點色，更把全身塗上泥漿，此照片更在網上廣泛流傳。另外，在《走過浮華大地》其中一集更以英國Punk造型示人，可見她不計較別人怎樣看自己把節目做到最好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rO33On\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rO33On&d=vsCEL2Mn6LjncruEp26GvAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=81df560b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rO33On</a><br />\n<br />\n正皮杜如風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮黃翠如 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81188be344e7faaf8304806700f04b96a764039c","tid":296684,"uid":4260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:55:09.000Z","msg":"黃翠如套地平線上勁好睇<br />\n雖然無豪玩豪食靚酒店之類既野，但好接觸到當地人既風土人情<br />\n輕鬆搞笑 好真實 之前睇完好迷佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢做旅遊節目主持人好自然 拍劇就不了"},{"pid":"de985f343dc86543371d1486d91b6640c99a0147","tid":296684,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"四十日峰狂嘆世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed768cbde382d8728e41774cbb90f5da52bbe810","tid":296684,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:26:33.000Z","msg":"香港公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ff57292a970aefd09f3fbc4260803789679155","tid":296684,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:28:42.000Z","msg":"洪永城"},{"pid":"cb32345fe7bbf2c848d2601c29f3a01e950ad492","tid":296684,"uid":91620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:29:50.000Z","msg":"打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果洪仔同翠如合體應該無人能敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e362cc34e0e6b577844a9f9c3539589dd7a1bd75","tid":296684,"uid":66239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果洪仔同翠如合體應該無人能敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁掉轉番，邊個男適合同社如風合作？"},{"pid":"5030261e08d44bfe6bfec314163d7723047e82e1","tid":296684,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:35:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd4941eb5b7f2c009d8ecd1d872317ac09ecd425","tid":296684,"uid":52513,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"聽杜如風講野真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"a8df5fca24cc4b350b992bae61355bd77ba4081a","tid":296684,"uid":62,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果洪仔同翠如合體應該無人能敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁掉轉番，邊個男適合同社如風合作？</blockquote><br />\n阮兆祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb12fed8cea264c46996d21edcc45922062b7560","tid":296684,"uid":33712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"翠如有線果期無人能敵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70baabdbd06d5a726316948b68857d23106715a0","tid":296684,"uid":90890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"我愛杜如風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d058be480d1d8c3d4251a12e7ef6fe880609fd","tid":296684,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"黃翠如早前為有線節目到秘魯亞馬遜熱帶雨林探險，她探訪當地原始族裔，還喝了由當地巫師炮製的巫師茶，據說這種茶有看到前世今生、跟自然通靈的功效，不過黃翠如喝了一小口就頭暈，更足足嘔了四小時，當時她還以為自己會死。黃翠如指喝完後出現幻覺，看見自己的嘔吐物變成兩匹馬和幾隻蝴蝶，現在還擔心會不會有副作用。<br />\n黃翠如又在38度高溫下在森林行了4小時，之後中暑暈倒，幸得當地導遊相助，拿一些草藥敷在她額頭上降溫，她才覺得好一點。<br />\n個杜如風山都未行過一步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊洗鬥"}]}